<table cellpadding=1 cellspacing=1 width="750" dir="rtl"><tr><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td><td class="QuranDataNumber" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" valign="top"><a name=1></a>1</td><td class="QuranDataArabic" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" valign="top">بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَـٰنِ الرَّحِيمِ</td><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" colspan="2" valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td><td class="QuranDataNumber" bgcolor="#F0EFEC" valign="top"><a name=2></a>2</td><td class="QuranDataArabic" bgcolor="#F0EFEC" valign="top">االم</td><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" colspan="2" valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td><td class="QuranDataNumber" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" valign="top"><a name=3></a>3</td><td class="QuranDataArabic" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" valign="top">ذَ‌ٰلِكَ الْكِتَابُ لَا رَيْبَ ۛ فِيهِ ۛ هُدًى لِّلْمُتَّقِينَ</td><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" colspan="2" valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td><td class="QuranDataNumber" bgcolor="#F0EFEC" valign="top"><a name=4></a>4</td><td class="QuranDataArabic" bgcolor="#F0EFEC" valign="top">الَّذِينَ يُؤْمِنُونَ بِالْغَيْبِ وَيُقِيمُونَ الصَّلَاةَ وَمِمَّا رَزَقْنَاهُمْ يُنفِقُونَ</td><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" colspan="2" valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td><td class="QuranDataNumber" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" valign="top"><a name=5></a>5</td><td class="QuranDataArabic" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" valign="top">وَالَّذِينَ يُؤْمِنُونَ بِمَا أُنزِلَ إِلَيْكَ وَمَا أُنزِلَ مِن قَبْلِكَ وَبِالْآخِرَةِ هُمْ يُوقِنُونَ</td><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" colspan="2" valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td><td class="QuranDataNumber" bgcolor="#F0EFEC" valign="top"><a name=6></a>6</td><td class="QuranDataArabic" bgcolor="#F0EFEC" valign="top">أُولَـٰئِكَ عَلَىٰ هُدًى مِّن رَّبِّهِمْ ۖ وَأُولَـٰئِكَ هُمُ الْمُفْلِحُونَ</td><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" colspan="2" valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td><td class="QuranDataNumber" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" valign="top"><a name=7></a>7</td><td class="QuranDataArabic" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" valign="top">إِنَّ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا سَوَاءٌ عَلَيْهِمْ أَأَنذَرْتَهُمْ أَمْ لَمْ تُنذِرْهُمْ لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ</td><td class="QuranData" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="images/left.gif" width="3"></td></tr><tr><td class="QuranData" colspan="2" valign="top"></td></tr></table>
